Package: glyrepr
Title: Representation for Glycan Structures in R
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bin", "Fu", , "23110220018@m.fudan.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8567-2997"))
Description: This package is a wrapper of 'igraph' for representing glycan structures in R. 
    It provides a set of functions to create and manipulate glycan structures, 
    and to visualize them in a graph format.
